<div class ="About The Science Department"> <h1><u>About The Science Department</u></h1>
<p class="About The Science Department"></p>
Eastside Academy has an amazing Science Department with a tean of dedicaed and knowledgeable teachers, the department strives to provide students with a well-rounded education in various scientiffic disciplines. Our Science department teaches the main science units that are  Chemistry, Biology, and Physics. Our department ensures hand on snd experimental learming opportunities for students, encouraging them to explore and conduct scientific experiments. Eastside Academy science department always tells students to use there critical thinking,and problem-solving skills. Our Department make sure our students go on 2 trips during the semester to keep our students interacted with the Science world.We enage our students to enage in discussions in class and experiments.
<br>
<div1 class ="Biology"> <h2><U>Biology</U></h2></div1>
<p2 class ="Biology"></p2>
In this subejct, Biology we study life and living organisms, including their structure, function, growth, orgin, evolution, distribution, and taxonmy. By studying biology there are a lot career options you could choose if yoyu studied Biology in school. Some jobs you can get are Reasearch scientist, Pharmacologist, Biologist, Ecologist, Nature conservation officer, Biotechnologist, forensic scientist, and Government agency roles. Students learn about various life processes and how various species deal with emvironmental obstacles.Here at Eastside academy when we are in our Biology unit at the end of it we dissect a frog which is very cool because we could see the frogs body parts and other body parts that we learned in class. Biology is important thing to learn because it helps us comprehend the funcctioning evolution and interactions of the living world's diverse species, including humans. Out of all the three sciences we teach here at Eastside academy students say that Biology is their favorite one to learn about.
